{"type": "article", "id": 22041, "title": "英国的一个公园里， KAWS 的大型玩具雕塑很亮眼", "description": "你知道 KAWS 吧？他在引领潮流这件事上还真是一等一的厉害。", "date": "2016-02-09T08:00:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 289, "name": "玩具"}, {"id": 7972, "name": "装置"}, {"id": 23235, "name": "公共雕塑"}], "category": 17, "author": 37534, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 102, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021322439174P8uSUedwvlQx.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>不久前，街头艺术家、玩具设计师 KAWS 为英国的 Yorkshire Sculpture Park <a href=\"http://www.creativereview.co.uk/cr-blog/2016/february/kaws-brings-giant-cartoon-creations-to-yorkshire-sculpture-park/\">设计了一个巨型的玩具雕塑</a>——这是一个巨大的、垂头丧气的气球卡通形象，恰逢雪天，雕塑身上落满了雪花，作为公共雕塑的一部分，着实新颖有趣。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021322397RgmOA69zL5hP3wY.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.49812734\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">KAWS 的公园雕塑作品</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">KAWS 的本名叫 Brian Donnelly，是名街头艺术家，也是潮牌 Original Fake 的创始人。他 1974 年出生在美国新泽西，12 岁起就对涂鸦产生了兴趣，但一直到 1991 年，才正式开始涂鸦创作。与一般涂鸦者不同的是，他没有在墙壁、地铁上绘画，而是将骷髅头画在了品牌广告画或海报上（比如 DKNY、CK 的海报）。</p>\n<p class=\"\">他通常将海报带回自己的工作室，画上著名的骷髅图案再把它送回原位。正因如此他又被称为“涂鸦怪盗”。海报一旦送回，很快就会被职员替换掉。待他成名后，那些涂鸦海报开始变得珍贵起来，聪明的广告主会主动将海报送给 KAWS 进行涂鸦，比如主打年轻市场的 DIESEL。</p>\n<p class=\"\">1990 年代，KAWS 赴纽约曼哈顿学习视觉艺术，并开始为一些日本潮牌设计玩具。后来他的设计范围渐趋广泛，包括轩尼诗酒瓶、Kiehl’s 的化妆品包装等等，他还和 Pharrell Williams 合作设计过香水瓶。</p>\n<p class=\"\">这不是 KAWS 第一次设计大型的玩具雕塑了。 KAWS 讨厌重复自己，也在一直寻求着突破。2006 年，他创办街头潮流品牌 Original Fake 将艺术和商业相结合，后来他还为 Kanye West 等一线明星设计过 CD 封面。街头玩具雕塑则是他近两年的新想法。以下是他之前完成的作品：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132239wH7hLYqa04bGFEzB.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">Along the Way, 2013, KAWS (Photo: Jonty Wilde)</figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132240HWDY8BVfpd5FaKj0.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">Final days, 2013, KAWS (Photo: Jonty Wilde)</figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132240YnVeUad3NkB0X7Mq.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.49812734\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">Small Lie, 2013, KAWS (Photo: Jonty Wilde)</figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132241b7f16BTwYRCocAlt.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">Along the Way, 2013, KAWS (Photo: Jonty Wilde)</figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132241RNG1hW7OKsvjpkbA.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Installation shot (Photo: Jonty Wilde)</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132242o6mPDwsIqVZSiY8a.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Installation shot (Photo: Jonty Wilde)</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132242v6gf3jGMxF4O7rK9.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Installation shot (Photo: Jonty Wilde)</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132243xwLYWleQ0OgVI5FE.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Installation shot of OriginalFake Companion (2006), Chum (pink) (2009), and Clean Slate (2014), KAWS (Photo: Jonty Wilde)</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p>题图来源：<a href=\"http://www.creativereview.co.uk/cr-blog/2016/february/kaws-brings-giant-cartoon-creations-to-yorkshire-sculpture-park/\">creativereview</a></p>\n\n"}